This repository accompanies our paper (if you use the software we would appreciate a citation):

Mickael Sereno, Stéphane Gosset, Lonni Besançon, and Tobias Isenberg.
Hybrid Touch/Tangible Spatial Selection in Augmented Reality.
Computer Graphics Forum, 41(3):403–415, June 2022.
doi: 10.1111/cgf.14550

