Server communication between the android and the hololens device for scientific visualization. Runs only under Linux.

Needed library:
    -github.com/MickaelSereno/Server_Engine
    -github.com/MickaelSereno/VTKParser
    -github.com/MickaelSereno/Math_Library
    -github.com/MickaelSereno/SciVis_Library
    -glm

Runs with 
    -github.com/MickaelSereno/SciVis_Android  (android  application - remote controller)
    -github.com/MickaelSereno/SciVis_HoloLens (HoloLens application - 3D visualization)

All the needed datasets (VTK datasets) must be in <binaryDir>/Datasets/

If a dataset is needed when running this program, a log message is written in the console
